quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,74,"Ciftoree tuma nde o wa…ónoo on lomtii…ďe Aadinkoo…ďe …ďeen, o weernii on ka leydi ho…óon njogitoo e ndantaaji mayri ku…ďeeje, ho…óon lesa pelle (wa…óon) cuu…ói. Ciftoree dokke Alla …óeen, wota on …ďurtinir ka leydi ko on bonnoo…ďe."
  7,75,"Hooree…ďe mbatu mawninkinii…ďe …ďeen e yim…ďe makko …ďeen mbi'ani gooŇč…óin…ďe lo'inaa…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe : "E ho…óon nganndi won de Saalihu ko Nulaa…óo immorde ka Joomi makko?" ∆Āe mbi'i : minen ko men gooŇč…óin…ďe ko o Nulidaa e mum koon"."
  7,76,"∆Āen mawnintinii…ďe wi'i : "Minen, kon ko ngooŇč…óin…óon, ko men yeddu…ďe …óum"."
  7,77,"∆Āe mborii ngeelooba ban, …ďe mawninkini gah e yamiroore Joomi ma…ď…ďe ndeen, …ďe mbi'i : "Ko an yo Saalihu, addan amen kon ko podanna…óaa amen (e lepte) si tawii ko a jeyaa…óo e Nulaa…ďe …ďeen"."
  7,78,"Dillaango ngon nanngi …ďe, …ďe mba…ótini ka ko…óooli ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe jiccii…ďe-…óaanii(.jus…ďe)"
  7,79,"O ruŇčtii …ďe o maaki : "eey mon yo yim…ďe am, gooŇč…óii mi yottinii e mon Nulal Joomi am ngal mi laa…ďanii on (reedu), konon, on nji…óaa laa…ďoo…ďe (reedu) …ďeen."
  7,80,"E luuti, tuma nde o maakannoo yim…ďe makko …ďen : " E o ngaray e paŇčkare …óe go…ó…óo goo adaaki on e mun e Winndere ndeen?!"
  7,81,"Onon ho…óon njottoo e wor…ďe …ďeen tuuyo ngaccon rew…ďe …ďeen! Si ko woni, onon ko on yim…ďe fantim…ďe(.…ďurtin…ďe)."